aima.core.environment.map
Class SimplifiedRoadMapOfAustralia

java.lang.Object
  aima.core.environment.map.ExtendableMap
      aima.core.environment.map.SimplifiedRoadMapOfAustralia
All Implemented Interfaces:
Map
public class SimplifiedRoadMapOfAustralia
extends ExtendableMap

Represents a simplified road map of Australia. The initialization method is declared static. So it can also be used to initialize other specialized subclasses of ExtendableMap with road map data from Australia. The data was extracted from a class developed by Felix Knittel.

Author:
Ruediger Lunde
